{"tid":444860,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"高普難忍怒火：我落場的話 卡尼攞唔到波","createTime":"2017-10-23T00:57:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-23T14:34:01.000Z","uid":32938,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"183c26a574b6438c11fc455596deb9bb96596014","tid":444860,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T00:57:48.000Z","msg":"利物浦再次因後防甩漏，結果1：4不敵熱刺。賽後領隊高普難忍不滿，直斥後防不濟，特別提到後衛洛夫蘭。<br />\n<br />\n洛夫蘭首先走甩哈利卡尼，加上門將米洛列特出迎不夠快，結果被對方攻破；到失第2球，又是這位中堅犯錯頂空氣，讓卡尼傳中給孫興民建功。差勁表現令他踢了30分鐘就被換走。<br />\n<br />\n賽後高普直斥：「第1球我們防守做得很差很差。第2球，反擊，當球越過洛夫蘭時已經太遲。如果這情況我是在球場，哈利卡尼就不會得到那球。」<br />\n<br />\n雖然點名批評洛夫蘭，但高普強調輸波是全隊責任：「我們要知道己隊要為劣績負責任，當然，我們可以糾正的，也必須糾正。整場比賽整個賽果都是我們的錯，熱刺踢得好，他們本分來的，但我們令他們贏得太輕鬆。」(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=rSimjt9jxvFkBhG6WqqG1b%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=6eb1b4dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"a2d3525afb15f1e3536ead47505735216fdae3a0","tid":444860,"uid":47132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T01:06:25.000Z","msg":"唔用洛夫 可以用邊個？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c79a1d3a264f553880a3621df9f9c9e2bb2dd6d","tid":444860,"uid":100275,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T01:23:32.000Z","msg":"屌仲以為係nine up報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a07b683ed4f23f92e01770588e5ee226c53b357","tid":444860,"uid":11254,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T01:25:47.000Z","msg":"自己唔買人中堅怪邊個"},{"pid":"c36e41a24eedc63ed9ad968307560c653356fd32","tid":444860,"uid":30040,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T01:30:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔用洛夫 可以用邊個？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢自己 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a06a01f1f37dbe9960a5a7a556583059213aa8e1","tid":444860,"uid":759,"like